state.unicode: [PH] S198 CE. Cao Cao conspires with Liu Bei to eliminate L Bu, who threatens to combine his strength with Yuan Shao and overwhelm him. L Bu scrambled to forge alliances to defend himself - first with Yuan Shu, and then with Cao Cao himself - but both times betrayed his would-be benefactors. Isolated behind the walls of Xiapi, L Bu sends desperate requests for reinforcements to Yuan Shu, to no avail.
